parameters: Prison Officer: Alright, get in here and wait quietly.
00_st_akane01_smile
Worker: Yo!
Worker: You've got a face I don't recognize. You new here?
00_st_akane01_smile

Worker: Hey, what did you do to get thrown into this
punishment cell?
00_st_akane01_smile

Worker: What's with you... sheesh... Can't you talk, or are
you just boring?
...Is there no one else brought here besides you?
00_st_akane01_anger
Worker: Oh, so you can talk after all.
00_st_akane01_serious

Worker: If you're asking about anyone else thrown into this
punishment cell, then no, there's no one but you and me.

Worker: Other than that, the guards occasionally bring
something that barely qualifies as food, but what about it?
So it is...
00_st_akane01_nomal

Worker: What? You got a friend here? There are plenty of
cells around, maybe they got locked up somewhere?
It seems likely...
00_st_akane01_nomal

Worker: So, what did you do? Get into a fight? Steal
something?

Worker: Ah, you've got a pretty good build. Maybe you killed
someone?
No way that's the case!!
Such a thing...
00_st_akane01_anger
Worker: Whoa, scary. My bad.
00_st_akane01_smile

Worker: Maybe I got you irritated. I've been alone in here
for a while now.
Worker: You could at least keep me company for a bit, right?

Ah, I see... You have your own circumstances too... I was
agitated, it was wrong of me to snap at you, sorry...
00_st_akane01_smile
Worker: Huh, you're quite polite. Well, whatever.
Worker: My name's Akane. And you are?
I'm Reisha.
00_st_akane01_smile

Akane: Heheh, is that so. Let's get along then, fellow rats
in a cage.

...Indeed. Meeting here might be some sort of fate. I'm
counting on you.
00_st_akane01_smile

Akane: So, what did you do to get thrown in here? This isn't
the place for small mistakes.

──... Due to a blunder, there was a collapse. People and
rocks were buried...
00_st_akane01_anger

Akane: Ouch... The bald guards here are especially greedy
when it comes to crystal ore. My condolences.

Akane: I don't know how much they trade it for, but those
who damage or destroy the ore they mine usually end up in a
bad way. Really bad.
Is that so... That's why the foreman protected us...
00_st_akane01_anger
Akane: Huh? It wasn't your fault?

The result is partly my fault. But a member of my team
insisted he was solely to blame and took on the sins of
myself and others...

I couldn't accept that... Although my time here has been
short, I can tell that this place is steeped in violence.
Taking on everyone's sins is like walking to one's death.
That's why I...
00_st_akane01_nomal
Akane: Hmm...

Akane: So you begged them, "Let us share the punishment but
at least spare his life," huh?
...Yes.
00_st_akane01_nomal

Akane: Around here, they'd probably call you a fool, but I
think it's a noble sentiment.
00_st_akane01_anger

Akane: Of course, that's if this place wasn't so rotten to
the core.

...I know. But I had to do it. Even in this hellish place, I
wanted to uphold my own beliefs, no matter how foolish it
may seem.
00_st_akane01_smile

Akane: Is that so. I don't know what kind of faith you have,
but it seems you were raised quite honorably, unfit for a
place like this.

I was honestly hoping that the girl who was brought here
would be in this cell. Although, I never intended to
exchange words with her.
By the way, you are...,

Akane: So, you've been put in this cell alone for a while
now. What's the reason for your imprisonment here? If it's
not too much trouble, I'd like to hear it.
00_st_akane01_anger
Akane: Ah, that.

Akane: Sorry for asking you all the questions. I'm simple,
you see. I tried to escape from here. "Escape," that's what.
Haha, I see. So you've been up to some antics as well.
00_st_akane01_smile

Akane: Well yeah♪ Escaping would have been somewhat
manageable, but my sticky fingers got the better of me.
While trying to escape, I thought I'd swipe some valuables
and got caught rummaging through the guards' quarters.
Ahaha.

Akane: It's not something to be praised for, but even though
I convinced myself that a skill is just a skill, the dirt
that gets under your nails always seems to show up at the
worst times, seriously.

You're tough. It's a brazen nature, but somehow refreshing
in this weary place.
00_st_akane01_nomal

Akane: This place is more secure than you think, and the
will to escape is quickly snuffed out in everyone.

Prison Guard: Hey rookie! I'm taking you to the boss, get
out here!
00_st_akane01_serious

Akane: Hey you. Are you going to meet with the boss of this
place?
It seems likely.
00_st_akane01_smile

Akane: Then listen up! My confiscated "tools of the trade"
should be somewhere in the boss's room.

Akane: If possible, could you find them and bring them back
to me?

Akane: If you can bring them back, maybe I can take you with
me, "outside."

Are you asking me to assist in your wrongdoing? Don't be
ridiculous.
I guess that's something you do with your own hands.
00_st_akane01_serious

Akane: You came to this dump, so you must have dirtied your
hands with something filthier, right!? Stop playing the good
guy now!

Akane: What's with you. So stingy. And here I thought you
were someone I could talk to.

Prison Guard: Hey! What are you dawdling for! Hurry up and
get out here!!
...Sorry to keep you waiting. I'll be right out.
